{"title":"ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.057Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements","updated":"2023-07-28T09:17:30.812Z","content":"<p>ERROR 1819 (HY000): Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements<br>\n出现这个问题是由于我们设置的密码不符合MySQL的密码安全策略，大部分情况都是我们设置的太简单了，此时我们调整一下密码安全策略即可。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#查看密码策略</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">SHOW VARIABLES LIKE <span class=\"string\">&#x27;validate_password%&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#此时密码安全策略等级为中、密码最小长度为8</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/7b1e9636b8ed421c875e4f6ef4c8fdfd.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#设置密码安全策略为低</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> global validate_password.policy=LOW;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#设置最小密码长度为6</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> global validate_password.length=6;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0943e2db914948449701759db769391c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#此时可以设置6位简单密码了</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">set</span> password=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;123456&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2726870244c0478895d50862b2765745.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"ERROR 1045 (28000)_ Access denied for user ‘root‘@‘localhost‘ (using password_ YES)","link":"2023/07/28/ERROR 1045 (28000)_ Access denied for user ‘root‘@‘localhost‘ (using password_ YES)"},"next":{"title":"ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)","link":"2023/07/28/ERROR_ ‘_usr_sbin_iptables-restore -w -n‘ failed_ iptables-restore v1.8.2 (nf_tables)"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/ERROR 1819 (HY000)_ Your password does not satisfy the current policy requirements/","reading_time":"230 字约 2 分钟"}